Cookbook

A recipe has:
+ Title
+ Bake Temperature
+ Prep Time
+ Cook Time
+ Preparation
+ Yield
+ Source
+ Image
+ Category
+ Ingredients, e.g. 1 lb Butter, 1 ts Fresh Oregano, 1 ea Bay Leaf, 1/2 c Black Pepper, 5 ea Garlic Cloves, chopped
+ Classifications
- Equipment, e.g. 9x13 roasting pan, cookie sheet, etc.
- Nutritional Content (Calories, Fat, etc)
- Notes

